attributes.review:
Listen. I would like to give the app credit for trying, but it stared into my cold, dead soul, and called me Twink-182. Not only that, but it literally took away half of my entire stick of toes that I prepared as snacks for the apocalyps. If I had to describe how this app will make you feel, I’d say it’s like if you poured vinegar into your eyes and tries to cook scallops on them. 
#ThomasSanders2020
